989
01:09:01,570 --> 01:09:03,561
Congratulations.

990
01:09:03,672 --> 01:09:07,369
Oh,just a little thing I scribbled
on a menu in a fish restaurant.

991
01:09:07,443 --> 01:09:09,570
And I suppose that menu's
worth hundreds of pounds.

992
01:09:09,678 --> 01:09:13,307
The price of fish has risen
steeply since the war, my dear.

993
01:09:13,415 --> 01:09:17,283
¤ She's got the kind
of shake that's irre-- ¤

994
01:09:17,386 --> 01:09:19,217
<i>¤ Irresistible ¤</i>

995
01:09:19,321 --> 01:09:21,619
- ¤ Kookie Twisterella ¤
- Hang on a minute.

996
01:09:21,724 --> 01:09:24,852
- ¤ She hasn't got a fella ¤
